prompts.user_prompt_template:
Generate a Weekly Progress Report:

Learner: {NAME}
Level: {LEVEL}
Week: {WEEK_NUMBER}

This week's data:
- Tasks completed: {TASKS_COMPLETED} / {TOTAL_TASKS}
- Current streak: {STREAK} days
- Speaking submissions: {SPEAKING_COUNT}
- Writing submissions: {WRITING_COUNT}
- Voice lounge time: {VOICE_MINUTES} minutes
- Assessment score: {ASSESSMENT_SCORE} (last week: {LAST_SCORE})
- Strongest dimension: {STRONGEST}
- Weakest dimension: {WEAKEST}

Provide:
1. headline: one-line summary (e.g., 'Great week! Consistency is paying off.')
2. wins: 2-3 specific things to celebrate
3. score_delta: improvement or decline since last week, with context
4. consistency_note: comment on streak and completion rate
5. community_highlight: note on participation
6. next_week_focus: ONE specific thing to improve (actionable)
7. milestone_progress: how close to level advancement (percentage estimate)
8. encouragement: 1-2 sentences of genuine motivation

Return as JSON. Keep total output under 200 words.
